28
00:01:58,570 --> 00:02:00,160
Aren't you going to ask me why?

29
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:02,470
Why?

30
00:02:05,490 --> 00:02:06,680
Because tomorrow,

31
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:08,520
