32
00:02:29,330 --> 00:02:30,080
Alright.

33
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:32,710
I'll come pick you up tomorrow.

34
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:36,400
Now go home.

35
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:37,400
Drink something warm.

36
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:38,360
Don't catch a cold.

37
00:02:39,330 --> 00:02:39,870
Okay.

38
00:02:40,770 --> 00:02:41,800
I'll go now.

39
00:02:58,890 --> 00:03:00,640
You should've given me a heads-up.

40
00:03:01,010 --> 00:03:02,520
I had no idea

41
