43
00:03:14,050 --> 00:03:15,430
Why is this umbrella here?

44
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:17,360
What's wrong?

45
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:23,080
He took it from Shen Jiahe's

46
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:23,520
place.

47
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:24,990
It's mine.

48
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:33,150
So?

49
00:03:35,170 --> 00:03:35,680
Chi Ye knows

50
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:36,870
I was at Shen Jiahe's house.

51
00:03:39,730 --> 00:03:40,920
What do we do?

52
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:43,240
Now that he knows you lied,

53
00:03:43,610 --> 00:03:44,750
